      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start, very formal. Can you make it a bit more intense though? I want him to really lean into the contrast between his world and theirs. Maybe have him describe the people themselves in more detail—how they look, how they behave, and why he thinks they're basically just living like animals compared to a modern society. Make it feel like he's looking down on them.",
